title: Update: How Does She Tell Her Sister She Doesn't Want Her Living In Her Neighborhood?
description:
Remember our listener, Jackie? Her sister has found her dream home and was ready to close on it. But there was a problem: the house was in Jackie's neighborhood. Her sister has no boundaries, and the last thing Jackie wanted is for her sister to move into her neighborhood.
So what has happened since we last spoke to her? We have an update!
